flowchart TB
    subgraph Payment Initiation
        P1[User Selects Plan] --> P2[Create Stripe Checkout Session]
        P2 --> P3[Redirect to Stripe]
        P3 --> P4[User Enters Payment Info]
        P4 --> P5[Stripe Processes Payment]
    end

    subgraph Webhook Processing
        W1[Stripe Sends Webhook] --> W2[Verify Signature]
        W2 --> W3{Event Type?}
        W3 -->|payment_intent.succeeded| W4[Create Transaction Record]
        W3 -->|payment_intent.failed| W5[Mark Payment Failed]
        W4 --> W6[Activate Subscription]
        W5 --> W7[Notify User]
    end

    subgraph Transaction Recording
        T1[Transaction Created] --> T2[Store in MongoDB]
        T2 --> T3[Link to UserSubscription]
        T3 --> T4[Update Payment Status]
        T4 --> T5[Cache Transaction]
    end

    subgraph Admin Operations
        A1[Admin Views Dashboard] --> A2[Get Transaction Overview]
        A2 --> A3[Filter by Status/Date]
        A3 --> A4[View Earnings Summary]
        A4 --> A5{Action Needed?}
        A5 -->|Refund| A6[Process Refund via Stripe]
        A5 -->|View| A7[View Transaction Details]
        A6 --> A8[Update Transaction Status]
    end

    subgraph Reconciliation
        R1[Daily Reconciliation] --> R2[Compare Stripe vs DB]
        R2 --> R3{Match?}
        R3 -->|Yes| R4[Mark Reconciled]
        R3 -->|No| R5[Flag for Review]
        R5 --> R6[Manual Investigation]
    end

    P5 --> W1
    W6 --> T1
    T5 --> A1
    A8 --> R1

    style P1 fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff
    style W1 fill:#ffca28,color:#000
    style T1 fill:#66bb6a,color:#fff
    style A1 fill:#ef5350,color:#fff
    style R1 fill:#4db33d,color:#fff
